50|$|The {{full-size}} Alphard Hybrid MPV {{qualifies as}} an Ultra-Low Emissions Vehicle (ULEV), achieving emission levels 75% {{lower than the}} Japanese government's year 2000 benchmark. The 2.4-litre gasoline engine has been developed specifically for use in <b>Toyota's</b> <b>hybrid</b> <b>systems</b> and features a high-expansion ratio cycle that raises efficiency and reduces friction.|$|R
